<pdd-reason>Formats a list of items as a numbered string.</pdd-reason>

% Write `pdd/format_list.py`.

% Requirements
- Provide `format_list(items: list[str], start: int = 1) -> str`.
- Returns an empty string when the input list is empty.
- Each item is prefixed with `{n}. ` where n starts at `start`.
- Items are joined with newlines; no trailing newline.

% Deliverables
- Code: `pdd/format_list.py`
